Robot Arm Host
===============================================================================

The robot arm host is a demo provider used to exercise non-browser host contexts.

It is a mock/demo host, not a general robotics API.

1. Contexts
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```text
robot://{instance}/commands
robot://{instance}/state
```

The command context supports provider-specific operations:

- `move`
- `grip`
- `home`

The state context supports `read`.

2. Pages
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- [Manifest](manifest.html)
- [Commands](commands.html)
